					item: "gtceu:nichrome_double_wire"
					type: "item"
				}
			]
			title: "Nichrome Alloy"
			x: 3.0d
			y: -3.0d
		}

		{
			dependencies: ["EE01000000000004"]
			description: ["Assemble four Nichrome Double Wire units into Nichrome Coil Blocks and replace the Kanthal inner ring of the Electric Blast Furnace. The EBF controller detects the upgrade automatically — no structural rebuild required, only the inner coil layer. At 3300K the EBF clears the processing threshold for Tungsten, Molybdenum, and several rare-earth elements that will appear in the IV tier. The coil swap is the cheapest high-impact upgrade in the GT machine tree: a few hours of wire production buys access to an entirely new material tier."]
			id: "EE01000000000005"
			rewards: [
				{
