			title: "Nichrome Coil Block"
			x: 6.0d
			y: -3.0d
		}

		{
			dependencies: [
				"EE01000000000003"
				"EE01000000000005"
			]
			description: ["Tungsten is extracted from Scheelite or Wolframite ore — process either through the Macerator to obtain the dust, then feed to the Electric Blast Furnace at approximately 3000K. Your Nichrome Coils operate at 3300K, providing 300 degrees of thermal headroom. Tungsten Ingots are the primary structural metal of the EV tier and the raw material for Tungstensteel, Tungsten Carbide, and the high-temperature alloys that compose IV machine casings. Begin converting Scheelite output to Tungsten Ingots immediately; the demand from EV machines alone is substantial."]
			id: "EE01000000000006"
			rewards: [
