		{
			dependencies: ["EE01000000000007"]
			description: ["The EV Energy Converter bridges GT's EV voltage bus with the RF/FE power network at the scale EV machines demand. EV machines draw power at a rate that overloads LV and MV converter infrastructure — build a dedicated EV converter bank near your machine floor and run EV-rated cables directly from your generator substation. All downstream machines, from the large-format GT multiblocks to the AE2 network you are about to assemble, draw from this bus. Size it generously; power deficit at EV is the most common factory stall."]
			id: "EE01000000000008"
			rewards: [{
