		{
			dependencies: ["AE01000000000007"]
			description: ["The ME Energy Cell stores AE2 network power, buffering the network against brief power interruptions and reducing draw from your main generator during low-demand periods. Place several near the Controller to prevent network dropout under heavy autocrafting load. The Dense Energy Cell holds 8x more energy per block than the standard cell — build these once your autocrafting queues grow deep and demand spikes become frequent. An empty Energy Cell is the most common cause of unexpected network shutdowns in complex factories."]
			id: "AE01000000000009"
