		{
			dependencies: ["41E155533627CFD4"]
			description: ["The Blood Altar's tier determines the complexity and cost of the recipes it can execute. Tier 1 handles basic orb infusion and low-LP sigils. Tier 3 is the first major escalation — it requires 24 Blood Runes of specific types arranged around the base structure and unlocks the Magician's Blood Orb, the Sigil of the Phantom Bridge, and ritual stones. The transition from a survival tool into a true magical system begins here. Expand the rune ring methodically: each rune type placed affects a specific throughput or efficiency modifier, and running the wrong configuration for the recipe wastes Life Essence at scale."]
			id: "BC01000000000001"
			rewards: [{
				count: 4
				id: "DB01000000000001"
				item: "lightmanscurrency:coin_gold"
				type: "item"
			}]
			tasks: [{
