				type: "checkmark"
			}]
			title: "The Tier 3 Altar"
			x: 0.0d
			y: 6.0d
		}

		{
			dependencies: ["BC01000000000001"]
			description: ["The Magician's Blood Orb stores 40,000 LP — twenty times the capacity of the Apprentice Orb — and unlocks the upper sigil tier and the ritual system. It is crafted at the Tier 3 Altar by infusing a regular orb with Life Essence at high cost; the altar must have sufficient rune configuration to process the LP demand without stalling mid-craft. The Magician's Orb is the inflection point of Blood Magic: below this threshold you are casting cantrips, above it you are running a soul-powered industrial support system."]
			id: "BC01000000000002"
			rewards: [{
				count: 4
