			title: "The Tier 5 Altar"
			x: 6.0d
			y: 6.0d
		}

		{
			dependencies: ["BC01000000000003"]
			description: ["The Archmage's Blood Orb stores one million LP — the maximum capacity in the system — and is required to execute the most demanding rituals and all Living Armor infusion recipes. Crafting it demands the Tier 5 Altar running at full efficiency; a poorly configured rune ring will stall the process partway. The Archmage's Orb represents the culmination of the altar upgrade chain: with it, your Soul Network functions as an inexhaustible reservoir. Cultivation disciplines lend themselves to this kind of patience. Fill it before attempting Living Armor infusion — the armor set draws deeply on every craft."]
			id: "BC01000000000004"
