		{
			dependencies: ["BC01000000000004"]
			description: ["Living Armor is crafted piece by piece at the Tier 5 Blood Altar, each component consuming several thousand LP from the Archmage's Blood Orb. The set is unique: it draws a passive trickle of Life Essence from the Soul Network rather than using durability, and it can be upgraded with Living Upgrade nodes that grant persistent bonuses — knockback resistance, fall damage reduction, swimming speed, or regeneration — depending on which upgrades are installed. A fully upgraded Living Chestplate provides more effective protection than any standard armor at this tier. The armor does not break; it grows with continued use."]
			id: "BC01000000000005"
